  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Time to Death</measure>
    <time_frame>Up to two years.</time_frame>
    <description>The time to death will be analyzed using Kaplan-Meier curves. Estimates (with exact 95% confidence interval [CI]) of the median and the lower and upper quartiles of time to death will be derived.</description>
